      "id": "PopularPost313557",
      "post_content": "It's an interesting idea. I'm not sure that using it on yourself is worth it most of the time since you lose the other two cards irretrievably, and it is possible they could all be critical cards. And forcing your opponent to lose two cards may not be worth giving him the potential game-changer from the top 3 two turns earlier than he'd have it otherwise.",
