      "id": "PopularPost338920",
      "post_content": "@Technicium Well spoken. I think you hit the nail on the head. On the other hand, I want to like this card for some reason. Ashnod's Cylix and [Foresight](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Foresight) could really see their day in the sun (and a significant increase in value) if we get more cards like [Misthollow Griffin](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Misthollow Griffin).  \nMore cards like Misthollow and this reads ![3](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=3&type=symbol)![Tap](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=tap&type=symbol): [Brainstorm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Brainstorm) and possibly keep an extra card (not too shabby).",
      "posted_by": "Phelplan",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost338920\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">@Technicium  Well spoken.  I think you hit the nail on the head.  On the other hand, I want to like this card for some reason.  Ashnod's Cylix and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Foresight\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Foresight\">Foresight</a> could really see their day in the sun (and a significant increase in value) if we get more cards like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Misthollow Griffin\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Misthollow Griffin\">Misthollow Griffin</a>.<br/>More cards like Misthollow and this reads <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"3\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=3&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Tap\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=tap&amp;type=symbol\"/>: <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Brainstorm\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Brainstorm\">Brainstorm</a> and possibly keep an extra card (not too shabby).</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '338920'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy97430\">Phelplan</span>\r\n                                (9/15/2013 2:52:02 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div clas